exports[`serializeText fixture snapshots > serializes branched-tree (branches-all) 1`] = `
"Birthday cake ideas
===================
Created: 2026-06-25 19:40 UTC · Updated: 2026-06-25 19:52 UTC

════════════════════════
Branch 1 of 2
════════════════════════

────────────────────────
Human

I'm baking a birthday cake for my dad this weekend. He likes coffee flavours.

────────────────────────
Claude

A classic **coffee and walnut cake** would be perfect — two sponge layers flavoured with strong espresso, filled and topped with coffee buttercream and walnut halves. Want the full recipe?

────────────────────────
Human

Yes, give me the recipe for an 8-inch tin.

────────────────────────
Claude

**Coffee & walnut cake (8-inch)**

Sponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 2 tbsp espresso, 75 g chopped walnuts. Bake 25 min at 180°C.

Buttercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1 tbsp espresso.

════════════════════════
Branch 2 of 2 (current)
════════════════════════

────────────────────────
Human

I'm baking a birthday cake for my dad this weekend. He likes coffee flavours.

────────────────────────
Claude

A classic **coffee and walnut cake** would be perfect — two sponge layers flavoured with strong espresso, filled and topped with coffee buttercream and walnut halves. Want the full recipe?

────────────────────────
Human

Actually he can't eat nuts — can you make it coffee-only, for an 8-inch tin?

────────────────────────
Claude

No problem — skip the walnuts entirely.

**Coffee cake (8-inch, nut-free)**

Sponge: 225 g butter, 225 g caster sugar, 4 eggs, 225 g self-raising flour, 3 tbsp espresso. Bake 25 min at 180°C.

Buttercream: 125 g butter, 250 g icing sugar, 1½ tbsp espresso. Decorate with chocolate-coated coffee beans instead of walnut halves.
"
`;

