exports[`serializeText fixture snapshots > serializes images (branches-all) 1`] = `
"What plant is this?
===================
Created: 2026-06-21 16:02 UTC · Updated: 2026-06-21 16:03 UTC

────────────────────────
Human

[Image (image/png)]

Found this growing at the edge of the lawn — any idea what it is?

────────────────────────
Claude

That looks like **creeping buttercup** (*Ranunculus repens*) — note the three-lobed leaves with pale patches and the runners spreading along the ground. It's common in damp lawns. If you want it gone, dig out the runners before it flowers; mowing alone won't stop it.
"
`;

